<div class="section hero">
  <div>
    <h1>Dashboard</h1>

    <p style="font-size:60px; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:-2px; color:#00913c;">£32,336.52</p>

    <p class="intro" style="margin-top:-10px;">
      Total in Zopa of which <b style="color:#00913c;">£32,183.87</b> is lent out at 4.76%
      <span class="tooltip" style="font-size: 0.7em;"><span class="top center">This is the average rate of all your money that’s currently lent out. It does not take account of any Rate Promises or bonuses.</span></span>
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: -7px;"><a href="#recent-lending-details" class="show-more"><span>Show</span> recent lending</a></p>

    <div id="recent-lending-details" class="info box">
      <table class="alt rows">
        <tbody>
            <tr class="new_funding">
              <td class="number" style="color:#00913c; font-weight: bold; font-size: 2em;">£10.00</td>
              <td>
                <p>
                  Last 7 days
              </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="new_funding">
              <td class="number"  style="color:#00913c; font-weight: bold; font-size: 2em;">£984.27</td>
              <td>
                <p>
                  Last month
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p><a href="">View loan book</a></p>
    </div>


    <p style="margin-top: -7px;"><a href="#queued-to-lend" class="show-more"><span>Show</span> money queued to lend</a></p>

    <div id="queued-to-lend" class="info box">
     <table class="alt rows">
       <tbody>
           <tr class="new_funding">
             <td class="number" style="color:#c95d3a; font-weight: bold; font-size: 2em;">£150.00</td>
             <td>
               <p>
                 Repayments queued (15th August 2015)
                 <span class="tooltip" tabindex="0"><span class="top center" role="tooltip">
                   Money repaid by borrowers in the queue to be processed and re-lent. Re-lending is prioritised ahead of new money and will be lent out faster.
                 </span></span>
               <br />
               <span class="hint">£1.13m from all lenders in 4 and 5 year loans</span>
             </p>

               <div class="position">
                 <div class="barchart">
                   <span class="graph" style="left: 27.889265831140722%;"></span>
                   <strong><span>Progress</span> 28%</strong>
                 </div>
               </div>
             </td>
           </tr>
           <tr class="new_funding">
             <td class="number"  style="color:#c95d3a; font-weight: bold; font-size: 2em;">£0.41</td>
             <td>
               <p>
                 Under £10 in processing
                 <span class="tooltip" tabindex="0"><span class="top center" role="tooltip">
                   New money and repayments will go through processing to be matched to borrowers. This step diversifies your money and gives you a blend of rates. £10 is the minimum amount you can lend at any one time. Smaller amounts will remain in processing.
                 </span></span>
                 <br />
                 <span class="hint">£827k from all lenders, ~£577k being lent per day</span>
               </p>
             </td>
           </tr>
       </tbody>
     </table>
   </div>

  </div>
</div>


<div class="section" id="earnings">
  <div>

   <h1>Earnings</h1>

    <span style="font-size:60px; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:-2px; color:#00913c;">£879.41</span>

    <p class="into">Total earnings including bonuses and after fees since January 2015</p>

    <div id="bars" style="height: 250px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 1em;"></div>

    <p style="margin-top: 0em;"><a href="statements.html" class="button minor">View statements</a></p>

  </div>
</div>



<div class="section" id="all-time">
